n><a href=\"/expertise/visualization\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\">data visualization and analysis page.</a><br />\n<span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\">If you are interested in commercialization opportunities and/or collaborative R&amp;D activities, </span><a href=\"mailto:nlfresco@alaska.edu\" style=\"line-height: 1.6;\">please contact us</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\">.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n',0,1400625485,0),('full_html::c54acd1c1d941dc738e60d0c213213d98cf8874688e7bbabd9434329c4ab2849','<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<div class=\"expertise\">\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"/expertise/scenario-planning\"><img alt=\"planning\" src=\"/sites/default/files/pictures/planning.svg\" style=\"height: 125px; width: 125px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<h2><a href=\"/expertise/scenario-planning\">Climate scenario planning</a></h2>\n\n<p>Quantitative analyses are expressed in scientific language. Qualitative scenarios use models and other information to explore “what if” questions and&nbsp;describe plausible futures</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"expertise\">\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"/expertise/communication\"><img alt=\"science communication\" src=\"/sites/default/files/pictures/scicomm.svg\" style=\"height: 125px; width: 125px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<h2><a href=\"/expertise/communication\">Science communication</a></h2>\n\n<p>SNAP publications and presentations make our work accessible to scientists, students, educators, planners, community leaders, media, and concerned citizens</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<div class=\"expertise\">\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"/expertise/visualization\"><img alt=\"data visualization\" src=\"/sites/default/files/pictures/data-vis.svg\" style=\"height: 125px; width: 125px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<h2><a href=\"/expertise/visualization\">Data visualization + analysis</a></h2>\n\n<p>We use projected and historical climate and sea ice datasets — and products derived from those data — to show relevant trends in climate at the regional and community levels</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"expertise\">\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"/expertise/collaboration\"><img alt=\"collaboration\" src=\"/sites/default/files/pictures/collab.svg\" style=\"height: 125px; width: 125px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<h2><a href=\"/expertise/collaboration\">Research collaboration</a></h2>\n\n<p>Our partners in academia, agencies, non-profits, and the community use our data and products to educate and create tools, or to join us in complex multi-year efforts</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n',0,1400625485,0);
